#: ../../source/acquisitions.rst:294
msgid "Once you have clicked 'Submit' the suggestion will be moved to the matching tab. The status will also be updated on the patron's account in the OPAC and an :ref:`email notice <notices-&-slips-label>` will be sent to the patron using the template that matches the status you have chosen."
msgstr "點選 '送出' 後，建議將移至匹配分頁。OPAC 讀者帳號內的狀態也被更新且送出 :ref:`電子郵件通知 <notices-&-slips-label>` 給該讀者，告知採訪的現況。"

